[SAM v1 — An example] The corresponding SAM format is:[The values in the
FLAG column correspond to bitwise flags as follows:
99 = 0x63: firstnext is reverse-complementedproperly alignedmultiple segments;
0: no flags set, thus a mapped single segment;
2064 = 0x810: supplementaryreverse-complemented;
147 = 0x93: last (second of a pair)reverse-complementedproperly alignedmultiple segments.]

